"\n"
"\n"
"[.description]\n"
"--\n"
"The interval of the blocked thread checker. The blocked thread checker periodically checks if any event loop or worker thread has been blocked for longer than the configured thresholds (`max-event-loop-execute-time` and `max-worker-execute-time`).\n"
